To deploy on a machine: 

Installation:

   git clone https://github.com/bhargavshivkumar/vimconfig.git ~/.vim
 

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    
    If gvimrc exists:
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule update --init
